Package: kohonenplot
Type: Package
Title: Functions to plot Kohonen Self-Organising Maps
Version: 0.1
Date: 2015-03-13
Author: Joris Gillis
Maintainer: Joris Gillis <joris.gillis@mobilevikings.com>
Description: Self-Organising Maps (produced by the kohonen package) visualisation. 
  This package provides a set of functions to visually display Self-Organising Maps (SOMs)
  produced by the 'kohonen' package. 
Depends: R (>= 3.1.0)
License: GPL v2.0
URL: https://github.com/jorisgillis/kohonenplot
BugReports: https://github.com/jorisgillis/kohonenplot/issues
Imports:
  dplyr (>= 0.3),
  ggplot2 (>= 0.9.3),
  reshape2 (>= 1.4.1),
  scales (>= 0.2.4)
Suggests:
  kohonen (>= 2.0.0)